name: HOLDER
description: Doggy is a memecoin that lives in the Solana blockchain. It was created as an experiment in the pumpfun streaming section to have fun, but it rapidly evolved as a symbol to reinforce the faith of the LATAM crypto community. Doggy is a dog that was born from the world of "El Holder" (a crypto newsletter with more than 4K subscribers) has been used for memetic communication and it gained the heart of most of the readers and followers in El Holder socials. Much bimsness, much profit, much wow.
